<template>
  <!-- <HelloWorld msg="Welcome to Your Vue.js App"/> -->
  <AppHeader></AppHeader>
  <main>
    <section class="container-fluid" style='padding: 0;padding-top:60px;'>
      <AppProfile></AppProfile>
      <AppProyectos></AppProyectos>
    </section>
    

  </main>
</template>

<script>
import AppHeader from './components/AppHeader.vue';
import AppProfile from './components/AppProfile.vue';
import AppProyectos from './components/AppProyectos.vue';
import AOS from 'aos';
import 'aos/dist/aos.css';
import 'overlayscrollbars/overlayscrollbars.css';
import { 
  OverlayScrollbars, 
  // ScrollbarsHidingPlugin, 
  // SizeObserverPlugin, 
  // ClickScrollPlugin 
} from 'overlayscrollbars';

export default {
  name: 'App',
  mounted() {
    AOS.init();
    OverlayScrollbars(document.querySelector('#scrollable'), {
      // className       : "os-theme-dark",
      // resize          : "both",
      // sizeAutoCapable : true,
      // paddingAbsolute : true,
      scrollbars : {
        clickScrolling : true,
        theme: 'os-theme-round-dark'
      },
      overflow: {
        x: 'hidden',
        y: 'scroll',
      },
    });
  },
  components: {
    // HelloWorld,
    AppHeader,
    AppProfile,
    AppProyectos,
  }
}


</script>

<style>
#app{
    font-family: Inter;
}
</style>
